matter to discuss.

05:53.287 --> 05:56.655
You two talk.

06:05.165 --> 06:07.499
Wanna see a
dead raccoon?

06:26.186 --> 06:29.454
How'd it die?

06:29.456 --> 06:31.857
Well sir,
that's the mystery.

06:31.859 --> 06:33.925
Sir?

06:33.927 --> 06:35.794
You're weird.

06:52.212 --> 06:56.348
My aunt says
you're home schooled.

06:56.350 --> 06:58.049
So what's
wrong with you?

07:01.955 --> 07:03.955
(knocking)

07:03.957 --> 07:05.724
Hello?

07:05.726 --> 07:07.125
Jonathan?

07:10.798 --> 07:13.832
I have your payment
for this week's dairy.

07:13.834 --> 07:15.700
Thank you.

07:18.305 --> 07:20.772
Was there
anything else?

07:20.774 --> 07:23.008
I'm a touch
embarrassed to say,

07:23.010 --> 07:27.078
I had a bit of a spill
out there, on your walkway.

07:27.080 --> 07:30.081
I'm sorry.

07:30.083 --> 07:31.917
Where's it hurt?

07:34.354 --> 07:36.455
Yeah.

07:36.457 --> 07:39.357
That seems OK.

07:39.359 --> 07:42.127
Just OK?

07:53.040 --> 07:54.940
She's occupied.

07:57.811 --> 08:00.512
I'm sorry.

08:00.514 --> 08:05.517
I'll be sure to salt the
driveway more diligently.

08:05.519 --> 08:08.153
So why are
you here?

08:08.155 --> 08:11.256
Where'd you
come from?

08:11.258 --> 08:14.326
I traveled through time and
space and risked life and limb

08:14.328 --> 08:17.829
to be here
right now with you.

08:17.831 --> 08:21.032
The city.

08:21.034 --> 08:25.070
Pushed my mom to the brink, and
then I was sent to Auntie Liz's

08:25.072 --> 08:30.008
scared straight farm, or
whatnot, for delinquents.

08:33.680 --> 08:36.348
You know the girls at school,
they aren't like you.

08:36.350 --> 08:37.482
What are
they like?

08:37.484 --> 08:41.152
Manufactured,
plastic, digitized.

08:41.154 --> 08:42.220
You're weird.

08:42.222 --> 08:43.221
Tell me to
stop then.

08:43.223 --> 08:44.723
St-.

08:51.832 --> 08:56.268
(music plays)

08:56.270 --> 08:58.937
Ugh.

08:58.939 --> 09:01.406
(music plays)

09:01.408 --> 09:07.312
I'll leave a light on for you,
in case you change your mind.

09:07.314 --> 09:10.582
(music plays)

09:10.584 --> 09:13.351
You've been alone
a long time, Jon.

09:13.353 --> 09:15.754
We both have.

09:15.756 --> 09:18.056
(music plays)

09:18.058 --> 09:19.691
Jon.

09:19.693 --> 09:24.796
(music plays)

09:24.798 --> 09:30.135
Christian,
are you OK?

09:30.137 --> 09:32.871
(music plays)

09:32.873 --> 09:33.939
Nepal.

09:33.941 --> 09:34.973
Bouton.

09:34.975 --> 09:36.575
No, listen to me,
George Leigh Mallory.

09:36.577 --> 09:38.376
First discovered on
the Everest expedition.

09:38.378 --> 09:41.279
It's Nepal,
I'm telling you.

09:41.281 --> 09:43.081
Bet me.

09:43.083 --> 09:44.182
Name it.

09:44.184 --> 09:45.483
Chicken
coup cleaning.

09:45.485 --> 09:47.252
Deal,
two weeks.

09:47.254 --> 09:49.554
A month.

09:49.556 --> 09:52.857
Flickered out,
Daddio?

09:52.859 --> 09:56.928
Nope.

09:56.930 --> 10:01.633
Oh, hmmmm.

10:03.870 --> 10:11.076
You are correct, Arielle,
and I was wrong.

10:11.078 --> 10:14.512
Next time though, sweetie,
always get a handshake on bets.

10:14.514 --> 10:17.282
Ow.

10:17.284 --> 10:18.917
Hi ya!

10:18.919 --> 10:20.919
Hi ya!

10:29.896 --> 10:31.963
(music plays)

10:34.134 --> 10:37.035
You know there's still time to
pull together a party for you.

10:37.037 --> 10:39.104
It's fine, Dad.

10:39.106 --> 10:41.006
Yeah, but it's
your sweet sixteen.

10:41.008 --> 10:43.642
If you say sweet
sixteen one more time,

10:43.644 --> 10:45.543
you are gonna
get a karate chop.

10:45.545 --> 10:48.246
Alright, I think I
learned my lesson there.

10:51.418 --> 10:55.020
So what's this
Christian boy like?

10:55.022 --> 10:57.455
Dark.

10:57.457 --> 11:01.926
Something out of
a detective novel.

11:01.928 --> 11:05.630
Smells nice
enough though.

11:05.632 --> 11:06.898
Did
something happen?

11:06.900 --> 11:07.899
No.

11:07.901 --> 11:09.034
We're always straight
with each other.

11:09.036 --> 11:09.934
I know, Dad.

11:09.936 --> 11:11.703
Not about this,
please don't make me.

11:11.705 --> 11:13.004
I'd never
make you.

11:13.006 --> 11:15.006
OK, good, because I cannot
talk about this with you.

11:15.008 --> 11:17.375
You can't talk to me about the
nothing that didn't happen?

11:17.377 --> 11:18.877
Correct.

11:24.818 --> 11:30.188
