13:26.873 --> 13:29.974
Yeah, I think so.

13:29.976 --> 13:31.209
You know, last
time we tried that.

13:31.211 --> 13:32.477
Yeah, I know,
she bailed.

13:32.479 --> 13:33.912
Whatever,
that was years ago.

13:36.616 --> 13:40.251
