over to Mr. Dhaliwal's farm.

14:17.991 --> 14:20.225
I'll be back
before you're asleep.

14:20.227 --> 14:22.660
Arielle, please, it
was just a nightmare.

14:22.662 --> 14:25.163
No, it was different this time,
there was a creepy little girl.

14:25.165 --> 14:29.067
Creepy little girl,
scary old lady, crazy mime.

14:29.069 --> 14:30.501
No.

14:32.973 --> 14:35.139
You're not
taking me seriously.

14:35.141 --> 14:36.941
Look, I know
what this is about.

14:36.943 --> 14:38.643
I know you don't
like being alone.

14:38.645 --> 14:41.346
That's not true.

14:41.348 --> 14:43.514
After dark.

