20:41.841 --> 20:46.444
I was under the impression
you asked for me to be here.

20:46.446 --> 20:49.046
Dad got a
hold of you.

20:49.048 --> 20:50.414
Was he not
supposed to?

21:07.133 --> 21:11.402
